      "translation": "随风而去吧"
    },
    {
      "time": 185.55,
      "time_str": "03:05.550",
      "text": "And I'll rise like the break of dawn",
      "translation": "我会如破晓的黎明般觉醒"
    },
    {
      "time": 189.03,
      "time_str": "03:09.030",
      "text": "Let it go",
      "translation": "就让它去吧"
    },
    {
      "time": 190.77,
      "time_str": "03:10.770",
      "text": "Let it go",
      "translation": "随风而去吧"
    },
    {
      "time": 192.73,
      "time_str": "03:12.730",
      "text": "That perfect girl is gone",
      "translation": "那个乖乖女已经无处寻觅了"
    },
    {
      "time": 196.62,
      "time_str": "03:16.620",
      "text": "Here I stand in the light of day",
      "translation": "我在此重生 迎着白日的光芒"
    },
